1
00:00:42,850 --> 00:00:48,540
♪Flower petals have fallen,
piling as high as mortal mercilessness♪

2
00:00:49,700 --> 00:00:55,410
♪Gone with the wind,
as if it has never existed♪

3
00:00:56,530 --> 00:00:59,960
♪I ask for more time♪

4
00:01:00,900 --> 00:01:03,290
♪To rewrite our stories♪

5
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:09,650
♪We travel together in joys and woes♪

6
00:01:10,180 --> 00:01:16,470
♪Blood bathes this entangled destiny♪

7
00:01:17,110 --> 00:01:23,260
♪For the next reunion
in the troubled times♪

8
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:27,380
♪We tread a treacherous path♪

9
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:30,640
♪To find each other♪

10
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:37,600
♪Wars and bleakness,
the bright moon shines upon the city♪

11
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:40,930
♪I will offer my bravery♪

12
00:01:41,190 --> 00:01:44,380
♪Fighting relentlessly♪

13
00:01:44,660 --> 00:01:47,630
♪All for no regrets♪

14
00:01:47,708 --> 00:01:51,348
♪In this life-and-death battle,
I will not back down♪

15
00:01:51,460 --> 00:01:54,910
♪Withstand enduring time♪

16
00:01:54,910 --> 00:01:58,130
♪Someone at the end of the world
never leaves♪

17
00:01:58,270 --> 00:02:05,210
♪I brave the grim haze
to be with you once again♪

18
00:02:05,210 --> 00:02:10,950
=Love of Nirvana=
(Based on Xiao Lou's novel of the same name)

19
00:02:11,190 --> 00:02:14,180
=Episode 27=

20
00:02:14,208 --> 00:02:16,662
(Yueluo)

21
00:02:23,220 --> 00:02:25,160
Later, take the family members away.

22
00:02:25,300 --> 00:02:26,390
Don't provoke them any more.

23
00:02:28,210 --> 00:02:29,610
But those bodies...

24
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,770
Lu Yu won't do anything to them
for the time being.

25
00:02:34,640 --> 00:02:37,540
I will take care of them tonight.

26
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:38,310
This is bad!

27
00:02:38,430 --> 00:02:39,040
This is bad!

28
00:02:39,990 --> 00:02:41,430
Elder Ji climbed over the city wall.

29
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,890
Get the things we prepared out.

30
00:03:12,370 --> 00:03:12,990
My son...

31
00:03:14,610 --> 00:03:15,150
My son...

32
00:03:15,150 --> 00:03:15,759
Go.

33
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:28,700
Let go of me.

34
00:03:28,740 --> 00:03:29,310
Quiet.

35
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,150
Trust me.

36
00:03:30,330 --> 00:03:31,050
I have a plan.

37
00:03:53,270 --> 00:03:53,960
Let me go down.

38
00:03:54,370 --> 00:03:55,330
Let me go down!

39
00:04:27,690 --> 00:04:28,600
General Lu!

40
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,040
Something has happened!

41
00:04:31,220 --> 00:04:31,870
What's it?

42
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,896
The Yueluo people
are transporting the bodies.

43
00:04:34,310 --> 00:04:34,950
What?

44
00:04:35,550 --> 00:04:36,370
They are right below!

45
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,490
Shoot them!

46
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:48,860
Arrows!

47
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:01,950
Come with me.

48
00:05:09,950 --> 00:05:10,690
Release!

49
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:12,900
Release!

50
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:19,220
Release the arrows!

51
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:29,990
Kill them!

52
00:05:30,450 --> 00:05:31,180
Wait, General Lu.

53
00:05:32,808 --> 00:05:33,630
Pei Yan,

54
00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:36,160
it was you who suggested
using those spies as bait before.

55
00:05:36,950 --> 00:05:39,220
Now, you want me to stop.

56
00:05:39,300 --> 00:05:41,570
What exactly do you want?

57
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:43,990
Given the current situation,

58
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:46,130
the Yueluo people have united.

59
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:47,920
It won't do us any good

60
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,570
if we attack them.

61
00:05:51,976 --> 00:05:53,560
Now that you have executed those spies,

62
00:05:53,570 --> 00:05:54,690
they won't open the city gate

63
00:05:54,690 --> 00:05:56,120
even if the bodies are destroyed.

64
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,840
Even after Yueluo is claimed,

65
00:05:58,072 --> 00:05:59,672
those people won't submit to us.

66
00:06:00,780 --> 00:06:01,550
Submit to us?

67
00:06:02,740 --> 00:06:04,340
Why would I even need that?

68
00:06:04,950 --> 00:06:06,100
If you can't stabilize

69
00:06:06,690 --> 00:06:08,160
the vassal land, it might

70
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:09,400
become a threat in the future.

71
00:06:11,540 --> 00:06:12,720
Yueluo can't hold on for long.

72
00:06:12,952 --> 00:06:14,180
We can come up with another plan

73
00:06:14,570 --> 00:06:15,810
to claim the city.

74
00:06:16,690 --> 00:06:17,740
Those bodies

75
00:06:19,100 --> 00:06:19,990
are useless now.

76
00:06:44,690 --> 00:06:46,570
Send them back
to their families properly.

77
00:07:09,990 --> 00:07:10,690
It was you

78
00:07:11,870 --> 00:07:13,180
who saved them in Qingkang.

79
00:07:15,100 --> 00:07:16,990
They intended to protect Yueluo.

80
00:07:17,610 --> 00:07:18,310
I was just

81
00:07:18,690 --> 00:07:20,040
giving them an opportunity.

82
00:07:22,780 --> 00:07:23,610
What opportunity?

83
00:07:24,660 --> 00:07:26,050
If the Liang's policy doesn't change,

84
00:07:26,780 --> 00:07:27,540
more Yueluo people

85
00:07:27,540 --> 00:07:29,050
will be sent to Liang State

86
00:07:29,050 --> 00:07:29,920
to be tormented.

87
00:07:31,944 --> 00:07:32,870
Reopening the case

88
00:07:32,950 --> 00:07:34,100
is the only way.

89
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:36,540
If that really happens,

90
00:07:37,740 --> 00:07:39,050
your identity will be exposed.

91
00:07:40,780 --> 00:07:41,810
I will make sure

92
00:07:42,750 --> 00:07:44,400
everything is arranged properly.

93
00:07:45,250 --> 00:07:47,130
If only the truth
would come to light one day.

94
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:50,250
I'm saying that you might be in danger.

95
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:53,340
You held me down with your sword
at the city gate earlier today

96
00:07:53,416 --> 00:07:55,384
because you wanted
to take the blame for me.

97
00:07:57,100 --> 00:07:58,990
I'm afraid everyone in the tribe
will hate you.

98
00:08:01,250 --> 00:08:02,240
Even so,

99
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:05,288
at least they can still
carry on with their lives.

100
00:08:05,810 --> 00:08:06,840
Carry on?

101
00:08:07,304 --> 00:08:08,340
I really can't understand

102
00:08:08,420 --> 00:08:09,740
what you're thinking.

103
00:08:10,780 --> 00:08:12,180
You should consider

104
00:08:12,740 --> 00:08:13,810
how to get back

105
00:08:14,110 --> 00:08:15,110
the jade hairpin from me.

106
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,280
Physician Jiang,

107
00:08:32,660 --> 00:08:33,760
these are today's supplies.

108
00:08:35,590 --> 00:08:36,800
It's snowing heavily outside.

109
00:08:37,180 --> 00:08:38,350
I hope the snow

110
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:40,088
can stop as soon as possible.

111
00:08:41,350 --> 00:08:42,760
Could you please inform Yu Lian

112
00:08:43,160 --> 00:08:45,160
to send more crow-dipper,
villous amomum fruit,

113
00:08:45,380 --> 00:08:47,000
blankets, and hand warmers

114
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:48,900
when she comes next time?

115
00:08:49,190 --> 00:08:49,800
Sure.

116
00:08:49,810 --> 00:08:50,500
Wait.

117
00:08:51,970 --> 00:08:53,680
Is everything all right
at the city gate?

118
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,160
Physician Jiang,

119
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:57,768
stay in the treatment area
these days.

120
00:08:58,070 --> 00:08:58,920
Don't go anywhere.

121
00:08:59,210 --> 00:09:01,060
Xiao Wuxia refused to save those
outside the gate,

122
00:09:01,190 --> 00:09:02,160
and all the Yueluo people

123
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:03,590
might give you a hard time here.

124
00:09:04,310 --> 00:09:05,640
He isn't that kind of person.

125
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:07,970
He won't be that cruel.

126
00:09:08,230 --> 00:09:08,780
But...

127
00:09:54,090 --> 00:09:54,780
Why is there smoke

128
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:56,040
hanging above Mingyue Valley?

129
00:09:56,570 --> 00:09:57,780
Jiang Ci said

130
00:09:59,050 --> 00:10:01,210
all infected items must be burned.

131
00:10:03,090 --> 00:10:04,050
Young Master,

132
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:06,210
have our people

133
00:10:06,210 --> 00:10:07,810
sent the message out?

134
00:10:08,330 --> 00:10:09,380
Half a month ago,

135
00:10:09,760 --> 00:10:10,830
we have already notified

136
00:10:11,160 --> 00:10:12,550
that shaman.

137
00:10:12,930 --> 00:10:14,280
This concerns Jiang Ci,

138
00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:16,090
so she will definitely inform the Yans.

139
00:10:16,590 --> 00:10:18,400
We must end the war

140
00:10:18,660 --> 00:10:19,760
before the Yans arrive.

141
00:10:20,180 --> 00:10:20,780
Young Master,

142
00:10:21,160 --> 00:10:22,500
at this point,

143
00:10:22,648 --> 00:10:24,380
not to mention
defeating the Zhenyuan army,

144
00:10:24,660 --> 00:10:25,760
Yueluo City

145
00:10:26,310 --> 00:10:27,690
might also be compromised.

146
00:10:28,760 --> 00:10:29,850
We mustn't lose it.

147
00:10:30,500 --> 00:10:33,900
Someone is more eager to end this war
quickly than we do.

148
00:10:35,160 --> 00:10:35,880
Young Master,

149
00:10:36,330 --> 00:10:37,430
are you referring

150
00:10:37,830 --> 00:10:39,160
to that person in the palace?

151
00:10:39,830 --> 00:10:42,780
Still, we can't place all our hopes on him.

152
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:47,470
We need to find another solution
to subdue the enemy.

153
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:01,930
Your Majesty,

154
00:11:02,210 --> 00:11:04,810
General Lu sent a missive
from Liangzhou today.

155
00:11:04,856 --> 00:11:06,728
He mentioned that Yueluo
is staging a rebellion.

156
00:11:07,090 --> 00:11:08,000
As the war is imminent,

157
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,550
he can't return to the capital yet.

158
00:11:11,660 --> 00:11:14,590
This is just an excuse to buy time.

159
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:17,330
If he could claim Yueluo
in the meantime,

160
00:11:17,760 --> 00:11:19,550
I wouldn't dare
to take action against him.

161
00:11:21,090 --> 00:11:22,050
Read this.

162
00:11:23,550 --> 00:11:24,550
Sanlang said

163
00:11:25,430 --> 00:11:27,000
Lu Yu took the liberty to attack

164
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,470
(Urgent military news from Wei Zhao)
Yueluo,

165
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:30,500
intending to occupy the land.

166
00:11:30,540 --> 00:11:32,210
They slaughtered the people rampantly.

167
00:11:33,050 --> 00:11:35,040
This is outrageous.

168
00:11:37,160 --> 00:11:38,780
Lu Yu intends to rebel.

169
00:11:39,736 --> 00:11:41,040
Please calm down, Your Majesty.

170
00:11:41,040 --> 00:11:42,160
Please calm down.

171
00:11:42,760 --> 00:11:43,780
Send a decree to Pei Yan

172
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:45,710
and tell him to assist Sanlang.

173
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,550
They must bring Lu Yu back to Qingkang

174
00:11:48,190 --> 00:11:49,830
using whatever methods they see fit.

175
00:11:51,590 --> 00:11:52,810
My Zhenyuan Army

176
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,380
mustn't be misused by him.

177
00:11:55,210 --> 00:11:56,430
Yes, Your Majesty.

178
00:11:56,430 --> 00:11:59,550
(Lord of Jianding's Residence)

179
00:11:59,550 --> 00:12:01,590
Lu Yu is driving Yueluo to a corner.

180
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:04,180
I wonder what His Lordship's plan is.

181
00:12:04,830 --> 00:12:07,570
Yan actually came up
with a rather indirect method.

182
00:12:08,140 --> 00:12:09,780
He wanted to bring Lu Yu down completely

183
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:12,090
using the war with Yueluo.

184
00:12:12,470 --> 00:12:14,300
However, even if
the Zhenyuan Army is defeated,

185
00:12:14,300 --> 00:12:15,950
the military reform still won't happen.

186
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:18,040
He should've chosen

187
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:19,570
the right battleground,

188
00:12:20,160 --> 00:12:21,950
not Yueluo.

189
00:12:23,900 --> 00:12:26,400
Madam, do you wish Lu Yu to rebel?

190
00:12:27,450 --> 00:12:29,660
I see an opening if he rebels.

191
00:12:30,950 --> 00:12:33,780
Lu Yu is too easily attached
to his sentiments.

192
00:12:34,300 --> 00:12:36,040
We have to help him

193
00:12:36,040 --> 00:12:37,672
let go of his attachment,
that's his son.

194
00:12:38,730 --> 00:12:39,330
Yes, Madam.

195
00:12:40,210 --> 00:12:42,950
However, before the reinforcement arrives,

196
00:12:43,140 --> 00:12:44,520
His Lordship might be in trouble...

197
00:12:46,540 --> 00:12:48,330
He's my son.

198
00:12:48,330 --> 00:12:49,970
If he can't even protect himself,

199
00:12:49,970 --> 00:12:51,400
he deserves the suffering.

200
00:12:57,470 --> 00:12:59,330
Did you come here

201
00:12:59,730 --> 00:13:01,850
with any brilliant ideas?

202
00:13:02,230 --> 00:13:03,780
I'm willing to enter the city alone

203
00:13:03,944 --> 00:13:05,330
to persuade Yueluo to surrender.

204
00:13:10,830 --> 00:13:11,920
What a joke.

205
00:13:12,160 --> 00:13:14,470
You want me to negotiate for peace
after what we've done?

206
00:13:15,368 --> 00:13:17,300
Dysentery is rampaging in Yueluo
at the moment.

207
00:13:17,540 --> 00:13:19,660
Many of the Zhenyuan soldiers
are infected as well.

208
00:13:19,970 --> 00:13:21,520
If we launch an attack now,

209
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:23,620
the sick Zhenyuan Army
won't perform well,

210
00:13:23,680 --> 00:13:25,420
and it will lead
to a heavy loss for you.

211
00:13:25,850 --> 00:13:28,500
If your goal is to claim Yueluo,

212
00:13:28,880 --> 00:13:30,680
you need to employ

213
00:13:30,680 --> 00:13:31,900
both tough and soft approaches.

214
00:13:31,970 --> 00:13:33,620
How about we set a five-day limit?

215
00:13:33,900 --> 00:13:35,830
I will enter Yueluo alone

216
00:13:35,920 --> 00:13:37,160
to persuade them to surrender

217
00:13:37,190 --> 00:13:38,680
and pledge loyalty to you.

218
00:13:40,040 --> 00:13:40,680
All right.

219
00:13:41,660 --> 00:13:43,680
We will do as you suggest.

220
00:13:44,400 --> 00:13:46,140
I will give you five days.

221
00:13:47,520 --> 00:13:48,590
After that,

222
00:13:48,660 --> 00:13:50,800
no one can stop me
from attacking the city.

223
00:13:58,160 --> 00:13:59,970
Young Master, Pei Yan is here.

224
00:14:24,020 --> 00:14:24,660
Thank you.

225
00:14:25,210 --> 00:14:25,890
Thank you.

226
00:14:37,432 --> 00:14:40,150
Physician Ling's prescription is
effective in combating the sickness.

227
00:14:40,690 --> 00:14:42,160
However, the condition of some patients

228
00:14:42,160 --> 00:14:43,350
is slightly different,

229
00:14:44,300 --> 00:14:46,020
so the dosage should
be reduced accordingly.

230
00:14:48,620 --> 00:14:50,160
The dosage of patchouli remains.

231
00:14:51,070 --> 00:14:52,520
Crow-dipper

232
00:14:53,230 --> 00:14:54,660
reduced by three maces.

233
00:15:15,710 --> 00:15:18,930
(3 maces and 5 taels, 4 taels of kudzu,
Chinese skullcap, peony, licorice)

234
00:15:23,160 --> 00:15:24,160
Ci!

235
00:15:26,050 --> 00:15:26,800
I beg of you.

236
00:15:27,090 --> 00:15:28,000
Please let me out.

237
00:15:28,040 --> 00:15:29,570
I need to see Physician Ling.

238
00:15:29,570 --> 00:15:30,310
Please.

239
00:15:30,680 --> 00:15:32,328
Ma'am, you haven't recovered yet.

240
00:15:32,330 --> 00:15:32,950
You can't leave.

241
00:15:33,090 --> 00:15:34,500
Please let me find Physician Ling.

242
00:15:34,500 --> 00:15:35,240
I can't let you go.

243
00:15:36,090 --> 00:15:36,660
Mother!

244
00:15:36,730 --> 00:15:37,970
Are you all right?

245
00:15:38,190 --> 00:15:38,690
Ma'am.

246
00:15:39,090 --> 00:15:39,900
- Ma'am.
- Move.

247
00:15:40,310 --> 00:15:41,540
Mother.

248
00:15:42,280 --> 00:15:42,810
Mother.

249
00:15:44,400 --> 00:15:45,300
Are you all right?

250
00:15:46,300 --> 00:15:47,400
Yu Lian?

251
00:15:48,730 --> 00:15:49,590
It's me, Mother.

252
00:15:49,850 --> 00:15:50,850
I'm back.

253
00:15:50,970 --> 00:15:51,680
Yu Lian?

254
00:15:52,470 --> 00:15:53,230
Are you all right?

255
00:15:53,230 --> 00:15:54,400
Is it you, Yu Lian?

256
00:15:54,400 --> 00:15:54,930
Yes, it's me.

257
00:16:04,730 --> 00:16:06,590
Physician Jiang also...

258
00:16:09,880 --> 00:16:10,550
Mother.

259
00:16:11,190 --> 00:16:11,730
Mother.

260
00:16:12,470 --> 00:16:13,710
Mother, wake up.

261
00:16:13,850 --> 00:16:14,520
Mother.

262
00:16:16,190 --> 00:16:16,900
Mother.

263
00:16:21,780 --> 00:16:23,180
Should I call you Wei Zhao

264
00:16:23,900 --> 00:16:25,500
or Xiao Wuxia?

265
00:16:27,690 --> 00:16:30,470
It depends on whom you seek help from.

266
00:16:30,536 --> 00:16:32,776
It's not necessarily my place
to seek your help, though.

267
00:16:33,330 --> 00:16:35,300
Wei Zhao has
the Pei Clan's account book,

268
00:16:35,660 --> 00:16:37,470
while Xiao Wuxia defends Yueluo City.

269
00:16:38,020 --> 00:16:39,090
Either way,

270
00:16:39,400 --> 00:16:41,190
you have favors to ask of me.

271
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:46,140
Shaojun, do you intend to trade a truce

272
00:16:46,310 --> 00:16:47,760
from Lu Yu for the account book?

273
00:16:48,620 --> 00:16:50,260
The war has to be quelled eventually,

274
00:16:50,500 --> 00:16:52,730
and we need to bring Lu Yu back, don't we?

275
00:16:55,350 --> 00:16:56,880
His Majesty instructed me to assist you

276
00:16:57,730 --> 00:16:59,310
in bringing Lu Yu back.

277
00:16:59,608 --> 00:17:01,496
I assume your burden
isn't any lighter than mine.

278
00:17:01,800 --> 00:17:04,020
After all, Xiao Wuxia
defends Yueluo City.

279
00:17:04,340 --> 00:17:06,690
He can't create another clone
for Commander Wei

280
00:17:06,820 --> 00:17:08,180
to persuade Lu Yu.

281
00:17:10,210 --> 00:17:12,710
Shaojun, stop beating around the bush.

282
00:17:12,840 --> 00:17:14,750
I would like to propose a deal
with you, Sanlang.

283
00:17:15,180 --> 00:17:17,860
I know you have a solution
to break through the siege.

284
00:17:18,140 --> 00:17:19,290
However,

285
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,230
you need time.

286
00:17:23,230 --> 00:17:24,430
Lu Yu is impatient.

287
00:17:24,536 --> 00:17:26,790
