289
00:17:27,990 --> 00:17:29,144
he will launch a fierce attack,

290
00:17:29,144 --> 00:17:30,840
even if it takes a heavy toll
on his troops.

291
00:17:31,080 --> 00:17:31,930
When that happens,

292
00:17:32,730 --> 00:17:34,210
the city will be compromised.

293
00:17:34,856 --> 00:17:36,200
