294
00:17:36,430 --> 00:17:38,120
I believe you will plan
for a retaliation,

295
00:17:38,840 --> 00:17:40,210
and that requires time.

296
00:17:40,450 --> 00:17:43,010
So does controlling the epidemic.

297
00:17:43,430 --> 00:17:45,010
I can help you to buy a few days.

298
00:17:45,710 --> 00:17:46,820
In return,

299
00:17:46,900 --> 00:17:49,180
you only need to hand over
the Pei Clan's account book.

300
00:17:49,600 --> 00:17:50,490
After that,

301
00:17:51,190 --> 00:17:52,990
I assure you that your identity

302
00:17:53,210 --> 00:17:54,560
will remain a secret from me.

303
00:17:56,840 --> 00:17:57,990
How can I trust you?

304
00:17:59,176 --> 00:18:01,160
You have no choice
but to trust me, Sanlang.

305
00:18:01,210 --> 00:18:04,030
Likewise, I can only choose to trust you.

306
00:18:06,340 --> 00:18:07,730
I will collaborate with you.

307
