in the treatment area.

315
00:18:40,360 --> 00:18:41,530
Young Master, please help her.

316
00:18:41,860 --> 00:18:42,560
Where's Jiang Ci?

317
00:18:42,760 --> 00:18:44,640
She was exhausted
from working day in and day out

318
00:18:44,640 --> 00:18:45,450
and fainted.

319
00:18:53,912 --> 00:18:55,272
Where are you going, Your Lordship?

320
00:18:55,430 --> 00:18:56,340
To find Jiang Ci.

321
00:18:56,360 --> 00:18:57,640
