370
00:24:30,990 --> 00:24:33,230
♪My love sees♪

371
00:24:33,290 --> 00:24:35,510
♪The sun rising and the moon setting♪

372
00:24:35,550 --> 00:24:39,710
♪Your face stays vivid in my mind♪

373
00:24:39,990 --> 00:24:42,190
♪Two hearts♪

374
00:24:42,250 --> 00:24:44,470
♪Bound to each other♪

