00:25:11,430 --> 00:25:13,120
All of you have misunderstood him.

385
00:25:13,900 --> 00:25:15,970
He isn't that kind of person.

386
00:25:16,660 --> 00:25:18,210
You have misunderstood him.

387
00:25:20,580 --> 00:25:21,930
Shameless Cat...

388
00:25:28,610 --> 00:25:30,850
♪I only wish♪

389
00:25:30,910 --> 00:25:33,130
♪For your unwavering heart♪

390
00:25:33,170 --> 00:25:37,350
♪You are still there when I turn back♪

391
00:25:37,450 --> 00:25:39,690
♪As passionate as we first met♪

392
00:25:39,730 --> 00:25:41,970
♪I hold your hands through eternity♪

393
00:25:42,030 --> 00:25:46,170
♪Time cannot separate us♪

394
00:25:46,310 --> 00:25:50,130
