00:25:58,660 --> 00:26:00,930
Go collect the herbs
according to this prescription.

396
00:26:00,930 --> 00:26:01,750
Ought to be careful.

397
00:26:01,990 --> 00:26:02,860
- Go on.
- All right.

398
00:26:33,352 --> 00:26:34,060
You've recovered.

399
00:26:37,440 --> 00:26:38,450
Thank you, sir.

400
00:26:41,078 --> 00:26:41,990
Let's go home.

401
00:26:42,160 --> 00:26:43,430
Finally, we're going home.

402
00:26:44,270 --> 00:26:44,770
Brother.

403
00:26:45,270 --> 00:26:46,880
Thank you so much, sir.

404
00:26:51,730 --> 00:26:52,600
We're going home.

405
00:26:53,510 --> 00:26:54,250
Slow down.

406
00:26:54,730 --> 00:26:55,820
Finally, we're going home.

407
00:26:56,568 --> 00:26:57,560
Finally, we've recovered.

408
00:26:57,560 --> 00:26:58,690
Brother is out.

409
00:26:58,690 --> 00:26:59,250
Mother.

410
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:02,930
Let's go home.

411
00:27:18,120 --> 00:27:19,530
Jiang Ci, you are awake?

412
00:27:20,270 --> 00:27:20,900
Well,

413
00:27:21,930 --> 00:27:22,750
