414
00:27:23,864 --> 00:27:24,790
Don't get closer to me.

415
00:27:25,580 --> 00:27:26,360
Don't worry.

416
00:27:26,770 --> 00:27:28,470
Physician Ling modified the prescription

417
00:27:28,510 --> 00:27:29,750
