- Thank you, Physician Jiang.

422
00:27:46,616 --> 00:27:48,170
You braved the harsh epidemic

423
00:27:48,184 --> 00:27:49,256
and were determined to save

424
00:27:49,360 --> 00:27:51,250
the people of Yueluo equally.

425
00:27:51,530 --> 00:27:52,690
Please accept my bow.

426
00:27:54,710 --> 00:27:57,290
