434
00:30:17,820 --> 00:30:19,030
I will go and check if any

435
00:30:19,030 --> 00:30:20,320
important prescriptions are left.

436
00:30:20,376 --> 00:30:21,016
All right.

437
00:30:21,060 --> 00:30:22,488
I'll wait for you at the entrance.

438
00:30:49,820 --> 00:30:51,180
It's hard to distinguish

439
00:30:51,608 --> 00:30:53,010
what the Shameless Cat truly means.

440
00:30:57,560 --> 00:30:58,450
I'm asking,

441
00:30:59,060 --> 00:31:00,920
when will we fly a kite?

442
00:31:01,320 --> 00:31:02,710
You fell sick and lost the kite.

443
00:31:03,230 --> 00:31:04,790
There's no kite for you to fly.

444
00:31:19,030 --> 00:31:20,490
Cats in the mountains

445
00:31:20,744 --> 00:31:22,730
