so close to my mother?

455
00:32:49,400 --> 00:32:50,490
She's your mother.

456
00:32:50,680 --> 00:32:51,900
Of course, I'm kind to her.

457
00:32:52,790 --> 00:32:53,690
You and your mother

458
00:32:53,790 --> 00:32:54,640
have finally reunited.

459
00:32:55,080 --> 00:32:56,180
I'm truly happy for you.

460
00:32:57,864 --> 00:32:59,144
Drink it before it gets cold.

461
00:32:59,576 --> 00:33:00,190
Give it to me.

462
00:33:02,952 --> 00:33:03,750
This is my favorite.

463
00:33:12,970 --> 00:33:13,680
Nice.

464
00:33:16,230 --> 00:33:17,160
It's still hot.

465
00:33:22,030 --> 00:33:22,770
What about that?

466
00:33:22,840 --> 00:33:24,030
Did my mother make that, too?

467
00:33:24,770 --> 00:33:25,860
Well, this...

468
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:28,360
I made this.

469
00:33:29,120 --> 00:33:29,900
Milk tea.

470
00:33:29,928 --> 00:33:32,200
Your mother said you liked drinking this
when you were a kid.

471
00:33:34,140 --> 00:33:35,420
Let me try that.

472
00:33:59,820 --> 00:34:00,430
Nice.

473
00:34:05,848 --> 00:34:06,640
Give that to me.

474
00:34:06,664 --> 00:34:07,250
I'll hold it.

475
00:34:07,420 --> 00:34:08,560
I haven't finished it yet.

476
00:34:09,060 --> 00:34:09,690
You take these.

477
00:34:10,312 --> 00:34:11,370
- Let's go.
- All right.

478
00:34:11,840 --> 00:34:12,580
Let's go.

479
00:34:17,690 --> 00:34:18,190
Hurry.

480
00:34:19,480 --> 00:34:20,120
Stay close.

481
00:34:20,610 --> 00:34:21,410
Let's go.

482
