489
00:34:34,008 --> 00:34:35,480
due to the tense situation last time.

490
00:34:36,776 --> 00:34:38,690
Whether or not the people
will be saved this time

491
00:34:40,080 --> 00:34:41,500
is up to Sanlang.

492
00:35:06,660 --> 00:35:08,000
What are you staring at?

493
00:35:10,290 --> 00:35:10,960
Yu Lian.

494
00:35:11,790 --> 00:35:12,580
Yu Lian?

495
00:35:13,810 --> 00:35:14,940
Where's she?

496
00:35:16,140 --> 00:35:17,040
In my heart.

497
00:35:22,100 --> 00:35:23,160
You asked.

498
00:35:25,190 --> 00:35:26,730
The person in your heart

499
00:35:28,020 --> 00:35:30,250
is someone who occupies your heart

500
00:35:30,730 --> 00:35:32,500
and thoughts all the time.

501
00:35:40,930 --> 00:35:44,450
♪Dare you fall in love with me
under the moon♪

502
00:35:45,010 --> 00:35:48,510
♪Embracing the fiery passion♪

503
00:35:48,890 --> 00:35:52,410
♪Dare you spend
the rest of your life with me♪

504
00:35:52,730 --> 00:35:56,230
♪Facing everything together♪

505
00:35:56,990 --> 00:36:00,490
♪Dare you promise me
a lifetime together♪

506
00:36:00,810 --> 00:36:04,310
♪Embracing me tightly♪

507
00:36:04,630 --> 00:36:08,130
♪Dare you stage
a fateful encounter with me♪

508
00:36:08,510 --> 00:36:14,330
♪Making a vow I looked forward to♪

509
